## Notion — Solutions DB (essential fields)

Title **Name**; Select: **Module**, **Type**, **Status**; Rich text: **Context**, **Description**, **KPIs** (JSON `[{v,l}]`), **Contact**, **Benefits_***; Multi-select: **Flags**, **Hashtags**, **Areas** (WORK/LEARN/HEAL/PLAY); URL **URL**; Rich text **Img** (emoji icon).

## Notion — Personas DB (essential fields)

Title **Name**; Select **Area**; Rich text: **FullName**, **Role**, **Quote**, **Motivations** / **Pains** / **Needs** (JSON arrays), **Steps**, **Color** (hex), **Emoji**; Files **Photo**.
